Step 1. Install node version 20.16 (version is optional) with the command:
curl -0- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
for Linux OS. Note:install it globally from your terminal.

Step 2. Close the terminal with the "close" command and reopen it.

Step 3. Install SASS by using the following command it you have node already installed:
npm install sass -v 3.7.4 (version optional)
